      <task >
        <statement>
	  <p> State the geometric effect that scalar multiplication
	  has on the vector <m>\vvec</m>.  Then sketch all the vectors
	  of the form <m>\lambda \vvec</m> where <m>\lambda</m> is a scalar.
	  </p>
          
        </statement>
        
        
